name: Pumpkin
bio: Loves long walks on the beach and sunsets. Catch me outside.

name: Ghost
bio: An albino direwolf who is new to Seattle. Famous for his role in game of thrones.

name: Bruiser
bio: Star of Legally Blonde, and Legally Blonde 2. A real diva.

name: Hershey
bio: Stay hungry is my motto. Don't leave food laying around, you might not get it back.

name: Bark Twain
bio: Surprisingly fast and will out-fetch you! Catch me if you can!

name: Puff
bio: Small but mighty. Not your average dog might be too stylish for you.

name: Larry
bio: Will steal your human and your toys. Loves a good bone.

name: Sithy
bio: Loves belly scratches in the park, especially in the summer when it's not raining.
